@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_evrtpt(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = (v2 / ((v0 + 0.63 * tmp + 0.59) * wp.abs(tmp + 0.93)))
    tmp = (wp.cos(v0) / (wp.abs(tmp + 0.64) / (tmp + 0.79 / v0 + 0.64)))
    v2 = wp.cos(wp.cos(0.62))
    v0 = (wp.exp(v1) * v0)
    v1 = wp.exp(0.05)
    data[tid] = v0
